PART 1: FIBONACCI EISENSTEIN NORM SEQUENCE
======================================================================

  N(F_n, F_{n+1}) = F_n^2 - F_n*F_{n+1} + F_{n+1}^2

  Fibonacci Eisenstein norms:
    n= 0: N(    0,     1) =        1
    n= 1: N(    1,     1) =        1
    n= 2: N(    1,     2) =        3
    n= 3: N(    2,     3) =        7  <-- Phi_3(2) = FORBIDDEN VALUE 7
